    "description": "<strong>THE ECDYSIS</strong> is an episodic Action/ Adventure game that immerses players in the life of Robin Jr., a professional photographer, guiding them through the thrilling adventures and enigmatic mysteries he experiences on his journey.<br><br>Play as Robin jr, a professional photographer who embarks on a journey to his dream place to experience and capture the nature and wildlife <br>but you know... not everything works as planned. As a number of mysterious events occur, robin has to investigate and find out what's happening around him.<br><br><strong>GRIPPING STORYLINE</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/21e7279e2b7c39d13f02028d0c896885.avif?t=1704457461\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br>-Engage in an exciting contemporary narrative and endeavor to piece together the clues to the fullest extent possible.<br><br><strong>CINEMATIC PLAYTHROUGH</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/f4f5dc25001a34bb99182bb6b01920fc.avif?t=1704457461\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br>-Embark on a cinematic adventure as you delve into the game, immersing yourself in its stunning visuals and captivating storyline.<br><br><strong>GO FOR A LONG DRIVE</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/20681b40dcdfbe9509d8cc2fae59b7fd.poster.avif?t=1704457461\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/20681b40dcdfbe9509d8cc2fae59b7fd.webm?t=1704457461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/20681b40dcdfbe9509d8cc2fae59b7fd.mp4?t=1704457461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Get your truck ready and gear up for an epic expedition to conquer the heights of the mysterious Mt. Mare's Nest.<br><br><strong>FIGHT FOR YOUR LIFE</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/0c8634fe90b0c19b6b21423f0f01c20f.avif?t=1704457461\" width=610 height=342 /></span><br>-Prepare to confront and overcome those who oppose your progress.<br><br><strong>ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/a4aeb1c027667b722818deed145c462f.poster.avif?t=1704457461\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/a4aeb1c027667b722818deed145c462f.webm?t=1704457461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1842880/extras/a4aeb1c027667b722818deed145c462f.mp4?t=1704457461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>-Enjoy a distinct original soundtrack and background score created by Kingsley Roy, an independent musician.",
